Click on the RNAi Design button to design Stealth RNA™ siRNA molecules. Up to 10 designs will be generated for your target sequence. The BLOCK-iT™ RNAi Designer uses statistical analysis of multiple validated Stealth RNA™ siRNA sets and a proprietary algorithm to select unique regions in the target gene sequence that have a markedly improved probability of success in silencing the gene.
